	<h1 class="title">越来越多检测说你的基因有风险，那谁来解决它？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/214916/small/214916.png?1443668287" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Denise Grady and Andrew Pollack</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-09-24 10:26:09 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/2534/medium/2534.jpg?1436651988" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


